name: The origin of billions of dollars

metadata.name: The landlord's stupid son
metadata.description:
Autumn moon, warm wind slowly.



Look past, is full of golden, this is the color of harvest.



On the ridge sat a boy, slouching, with a weed dangling from his mouth, squinting at the hard-working peasants.



A burst of footsteps, startled the young, the young turned to see the man, a bit proud smile on his face said: "Yang Lao, look at your face, should be a good harvest! How about that? The statistics are ready."
